verbose_text: Analysis of pre- and mature miRNA levels of over-expressing KSRP cells, previously shown to promote the transition from pri to pre for several miRNAs, indicated that seven out of the ten miRNAs (miR-106b, miR-193b, miR-196b, miR-21, miR-224, miR-23b and miR-25) showed a variable decrease in the levels of both pre and mature forms (XREF_FIG).
